       <i> Gilligan's Isle"]</i>

00:03.537 --> 00:05.804
¶ Just sit right back
    and you'll hear a tale ¶

00:05.873 --> 00:08.006
¶ A tale of a fateful trip ¶

00:08.074 --> 00:10.476
¶ That started
    from this tropic port ¶

00:10.544 --> 00:12.610
¶ Aboard this tiny ship ¶

00:12.679 --> 00:14.979
¶ The mate was
     a mighty sailin' man ¶

00:15.048 --> 00:17.516
¶ The Skipper brave and sure ¶

00:17.585 --> 00:19.418
¶ Five passengers
      set sail that day ¶

00:19.486 --> 00:22.087
¶ For a three-hour tour ¶

00:22.156 --> 00:25.156
¶ A three-hour tour ¶

00:25.225 --> 00:26.591
[thunder rumbling]

00:26.660 --> 00:28.960
¶ The weather started
     getting rough ¶

00:29.029 --> 00:31.597
¶ The tiny ship was tossed ¶

00:31.665 --> 00:34.132
¶ If not for the courage
    of the fearless crew ¶

00:34.201 --> 00:35.934
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

00:36.003 --> 00:38.236
¶ The Minnow would be lost ¶

