¶ The ship set ground
     on the shore ¶

00:40.407 --> 00:43.041
¶ Of this uncharted
      desert isle ¶

00:43.110 --> 00:45.443
¶ With Gilligan ¶

00:45.512 --> 00:47.845
¶ The Skipper too ¶

00:47.914 --> 00:49.915
¶ The millionaire ¶

00:49.984 --> 00:52.283
¶ And his wife ¶

00:52.352 --> 00:55.086
¶ The movie star ¶

00:55.155 --> 00:56.889
¶ And the rest ¶

